room_title: Escape room "Treasure Hunt" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
room_description: Are you ready for an adventure, mates… straight to Davy Jones’ locker? Well, shiver me timbers. Explore the caverns along Barataria Cove where the likes of Jean Lafitte once sailed and buried his pirate treasures. Find the treasure map, follow the clues, solve the riddles, and find the treasure before escaping in an hour!
